column5: Hey anyone out there got a digital file of the 2001 - 2005 stocking lists for Minden/Haliburton....I lost my digital file in the abyss of my hard drive...any help would be appreciated....and wasn't smart enough to print off a copy  Brkygetrr
If you call the MNR office for that region they should be able to help you out.  I have had them fax me maps/lists/etc before.  Cheers, Tony

right o Tony...thanks I'll give that a try though without a fax handy it may be difficult..lol.. I may just end up driving up there during the week some time and stop in to the office...worst aprt is I was just there last week and only picked up the new list...that'll teach me for trusting the technology and not the ol' fashioned paper system...    hey Troutologist...you can get me at [emailÂ protected]'ll send ya 06' once I get your address  Brkygetrr
brkygettr...I will try and scan then on my computer and send them to you.
I would love a copy too. Lost mine when my computer crashed two years ago.
